headline: EA SPORTS™ NHL® 26 Launches Worldwide Today, Bringing Fans an Early Start to the Hockey Season
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., September 12, 2025--Today, Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) launches EA SPORTS™ NHL® 26 worldwide on PlayStation®5 and Xbox Series X|S, inviting players and hockey fans everywhere to say "Check My Game" and show off their own skill, swagger, and stories.
